=== 開發 ===
2018年3月8日，BBC宣布[[湯姆·霍伯|湯姆·霍伯]]已簽約成為[[導演|導演]]，此外[[達芙妮·金|達芙妮·金]]將飾演女主角[[萊拉·貝拉克|萊拉·貝拉克]]，[[林-曼努爾·米蘭達|林-曼努爾·米蘭達]]將飾演冒險家[[李·史科比|李·史科比]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2018/03/the-kings-speech-director-tom-hooper-logan-star-sign-up-for-his-dark-materials-adaptation-1202319285/|title=‘The King’s Speech’ Director Tom Hooper & ‘Logan’ Star Dafne Keen Sign Up For ‘His Dark Materials’ Adaptation|last=Wiseman|first=Peter White,Andreas|date=2018-03-08|newspaper=Deadline|accessdate=2018-09-17|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-08-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180805112624/https://deadline.com/2018/03/the-kings-speech-director-tom-hooper-logan-star-sign-up-for-his-dark-materials-adaptation-1202319285/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年6月8日，宣布了[[占士·麥艾禾|占士·麥艾禾]]、[[克拉克·彼得斯|克拉克·彼得斯]]和[[露絲·威爾遜|露絲·威爾遜]]已經簽約加入演員陣容<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://deadline.com/2018/06/james-mcavoy-clarke-peters-sign-up-to-bbc-one-fantasy-drama-his-dark-materials-1202406102/|title=James McAvoy & Clarke Peters Sign Up To BBC One Fantasy Drama ‘His Dark Materials’|last=White|first=Peter|date=2018-06-08|newspaper=Deadline|accessdate=2018-09-17|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621162547/https://deadline.com/2018/06/james-mcavoy-clarke-peters-sign-up-to-bbc-one-fantasy-drama-his-dark-materials-1202406102/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月27日，BBC正式公佈選角<ref name="Cast">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2018/his-dark-materials|title=BBC and Bad Wolf unveil cast and creative team of His Dark Materials|website=BBC Media Centre|date=2018-07-27|accessdate=2018-08-13|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190517203425/https://www.bbc.co.uk/mediacentre/latestnews/2018/his-dark-materials|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月，《[[廣播時報|廣播時報]]》透露，[[露塔·格德米納斯|露塔·格德米納斯]]將飾演女巫女王[[席拉芬娜·帕可拉|席拉芬娜·帕可拉]]的角色<ref name=":0" />。

